- Confirmation-dialog screenshot: `[LINK TO SCREENSHOT]`
- Transition Pending screenshot: `[LINK TO SCREENSHOT]`
- Serial log: `[LINK OR INLINE LOG]`
- Failing firmware commit: `[ENTER SHA]`
- Issue/correction reference: `[ENTER COMMIT, ISSUE, OR DOCUMENT LINK]`

